      |:  [[face=`@tas`%$ sur=`path`/] [subject=`vase`!>(..zuse) ca-scry-cache=ca-scry-cache:state]]
      ?:  =(%test-globals face)
        !!  ::  TODO: do better  [[%| '%test-globals face is reserved'] state]
